 ﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄ
   Release Notes:

   Final Dusk is a unique combination of puzzle and action game. Each       
   level consists of two distinct phases. First you need to manipulate      
   the environment using multiple powers to create a safe path for          
   Vampire Princess Mina. In the second phase you need to actively          
   protect Mina on her way to her goal. As you advance you'll discover      
   new locations and learn new powers which you must combine to be able     
   to complete each level and learn the story of the princess and her       
   beloved kingdom.                                                         
                                                                            
   A wicked curse has fallen on the people of the Kingdom of Vempire -      
   everyone has turned to stone! It痴 up to Mina, the vampire princess,     
   to travel through her kingdom to the evil witch痴 tower to reverse the   
   curse.                                                                   
                                                                            
   4 completely unique chapters                                             
   80 levels                                                                
   4 different powers, each with two modes                                  
   Hand-crafted, logic and action-based puzzles                             
   Multiple ways to solve the puzzles                                       
   Challenging bosses                                                       
   User-friendly interface                                                  
   Funny and interesting story                                              
   Lovely manga art style                                                   
   Beautiful 2D animations                                                  
                                                                            
                                                                            
   RIPPED: Nothing                                                          
 ﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄ
